questions.name: Q-1
questions.question_usr: Q: Generate an esoteric french phrase. (Then explain why it would be considered esoteric) A:
questions.completion:
"Les étoiles dansent avec les murmures du vent"

This phrase could be considered esoteric because it combines elements of nature (stars and wind) with a sense of movement and mysticism. It evokes a sense of poetic imagery and symbolism that may not be easily understood by those unfamiliar with French language or culture. Additionally, the phrase does not have a clear literal meaning, leaving room for interpretation and personal reflection.
